"""
AeroLIT bootstrap network helper.

This helper walks a user through the network choices needed by bootstrap.sh and
writes reviewable executable scripts next to bootstrap.sh. By default, it does
not change the system or run bootstrap.sh.

Python compatibility note:
  This script intentionally supports Python 3.6+ for RHEL 8/platform-python.
  Avoid Python 3.9+ syntax such as list[str] and Python 3.10+ syntax such as
  str | None.

Supported bootstrap network options covered by this helper:
  --skip-pxe
  --skip-controller
  --pxe-server-ip
  --pxe-http-port
  --pxe-interface
  --pxe-dhcp-start
  --pxe-dhcp-end
  --pxe-dhcp-netmask
  --pxe-gateway
  --pxe-dns
  --nfs-server-ip
  --nfs-allow-clients
  --nfs-allow-all-clients
"""

